r  Graf von Truhendingen est né environ 1168, à Autriche, son père, Graf Friedrich II von Truhendingen, avait 32 ans et sa mère, Mrs. Graf Friedrich II, avait 30 ans. Il a eu au moins 1 fils et 1 fille avec Eufemia Von Hirscher. Il est décédé en 1198, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 31 ans."},"de":{"about 1168–1198":"um 1168–1198","1168–1198":"1168–1198","1166–1229":"1166–1229","1189–1253":"1189–1253","1198–Female":"1198–Verstorben","1137–1184":"1137–1184","1140–Female":"1140–Verstorben","1137":"1137","1168":"1168","1189":"1189","1166":"1166","1198":"1198","1253":"1253","about 1168":"um 1168","1195":"1184","1140":"1140","1184":"1184","about 1198":"um 1198","1229":"1229","Truhendingen, Austria":"Österreich","Switzerland":"Schweiz","lifeSummary":"Als Friedrich III von Truhendingen Edelfreier  Graf von Truhendingen um 1168 in Österreich geboren wurde, war sein Vater Graf Friedrich II von Truhendingen 32 und seine Mutter Mrs. Graf Friedrich II 30. Er hatte mit Eufemia Von Hirscher mindestens 1 Sohn und 1 Tochter. Er starb 1198 im Alter von 31 Jahren in seinem Geburtsort."},"ht":{"about 1168–1198":"about 1168–1198","1168–1198":"1168–1198","1166–1229":"1166–1229","1189–1253":"1189–1253","1198–Female":"1198–Desede","1137–1184":"1137–1184","1140–Female":"1140–Desede","1137":"1137","1168":"1168","1189":"1189","1166":"1166","1198":"1198","1253":"1253","about 1168":"about 1168","1195":"1184","1140":"1140","1184":"1184","about 1198":"about 1198","1229":"1229","Truhendingen, Austria":"Otrich","Switzerland":"Suisse"},"hu":{"about 1168–1198":"1168 körül–1198","1168–1198":"1168–1198","1166–1229":"1166–1229","1189–1253":"1189–1253","1198–Female":"1198–elhunyt","1137–1184":"1137–1184","1140–Female":"1140–elhunyt","1137":"1137","1168":"1168","1189":"1189","1166":"1166","1198":"1198","1253":"1253","about 1168":"1168 körül","1195":"1184","1140":"1140","1184":"1184","about 1198":"1198 körül","1229":"1229","Truhendingen, Austria":"Ausztria","Switzerland":"Svájc"},"id":{"about 1168–1198":